---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Predictions" description="9 blind predictions, 14 falsified claims, 8 testable predictions with explicit falsification criteria.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Predictions Registry</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10">Blind predictions locked before measurement, falsified claims documented honestly, and upcoming experimental tests.</p>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-green">9</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Blind Predictions</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">12</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Sub-10 ppm</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-400">14</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Falsified</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-400">8</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Testable Now</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Blind Predictions -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-green rounded-full"></span>
        Blind Predictions (Strongest Evidence)
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Made BEFORE checking measured values. These carry no look-elsewhere penalty. Combined P-value: ~2.5 &times; 10<sup>-7</sup>.</p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
              <th class="text-left text-gray-400 font-medium py-2 pr-4">Prediction</th>
              <th class="text-left text-gray-400 font-medium py-2 pr-4">Precision</th>
              <th class="text-left text-gray-400 font-medium py-2">Sigma</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-gray-300">
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">100&middot;&Omega;<sub>b</sub>h&sup2;</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0.77%</td><td class="py-2 text-accent-green">&lt;1&sigma;</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">100&middot;&Omega;<sub>c</sub>h&sup2;</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0.34%</td><td class="py-2 text-accent-green">&lt;1&sigma;</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">100&middot;&theta;<sub>s</sub></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0.13%</td><td class="py-2 text-accent-yellow">2.1&sigma;</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">ln(10<sup>10</sup>A<sub>s</sub>)</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0.006%</td><td class="py-2 text-accent-green">&lt;1&sigma;</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Spectral index n<sub>s</sub></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0.010%</td><td class="py-2 text-accent-green">&lt;1&sigma;</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Reionization optical depth &tau;</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0.79%</td><td class="py-2 text-accent-green">&lt;1&sigma;</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">CMB shift parameter R</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0.035%</td><td class="py-2 text-accent-green">&lt;1&sigma;</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Neutrino mass ratio R<sub>31</sub></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">1.7%</td><td class="py-2 text-accent-green">0.62&sigma;</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4">Neutrino mass ratio R<sub>32</sub></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">1.8%</td><td class="py-2 text-accent-green">0.64&sigma;</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-3">6/7 CMB predictions within 1&sigma;. 2/2 neutrino predictions within 1&sigma;.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Near-Term Tests -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-brand-500 rounded-full"></span>
        Near-Term Experimental Tests
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Each prediction has explicit falsification criteria. These are clean kills, not "we can adjust" situations.</p>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-3">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-white font-medium text-sm">Dark matter mass</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs">m<sub>DM</sub> = m<sub>e</sub> &times; (n<sub>c</sub>-1)<sup>n<sub>d</sub></sup> = <strong class="text-white">5.11 GeV</strong></div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">SuperCDMS 2026&ndash;2027</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-3">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-white font-medium text-sm">Tensor-to-scalar ratio</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs"><strong class="text-white">r = 0.035</strong> (= Im<sub>O</sub>/200 = 7/200)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">CMB-S4 ~2028</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-3">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-white font-medium text-sm">95 GeV scalar particle</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Framework predicts <strong class="text-white">NO</strong></div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">LHC Run 3 (now)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-3">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-white font-medium text-sm">Neutrino mass ordering</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs"><strong class="text-white">Normal</strong>, with m<sub>1</sub> = 0</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">JUNO ~2027</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-3">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-white font-medium text-sm">Dark energy equation of state</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs"><strong class="text-white">w = -1</strong> exactly</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">DESI (ongoing)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-3">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-white font-medium text-sm">Colored pNGBs</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs"><strong class="text-white">~1761 GeV</strong> from Coleman-Weinberg potential</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">HL-LHC 2026&ndash;2029</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Falsified Claims -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-400 rounded-full"></span>
        Falsified Claims (14 total)
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Recording failures is essential. We don't hide what doesn't work.</p>
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-700">
                <th class="text-left text-gray-400 font-medium py-2 pr-3">Type</th>
                <th class="text-left text-gray-400 font-medium py-2 pr-3">Count</th>
                <th class="text-left text-gray-400 font-medium py-2">Examples</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-gray-300">
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-3">Definitively falsified</td><td class="py-2 pr-3 font-mono">9</td><td class="py-2 text-gray-400">sin&sup2;&theta;<sub>W</sub>=2/25 (65% wrong), higher CMB peaks (12-19% off)</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-3">Deprecated</td><td class="py-2 pr-3 font-mono">4</td><td class="py-2 text-gray-400">G from |&Pi;|, EFE from &gamma;</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-2 pr-3">Withdrawn</td><td class="py-2 pr-3 font-mono">1</td><td class="py-2 text-gray-400">h(&gamma;) novelty claim</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/explore" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
        Browse All 37 Predictions
        <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-4">Interactive explorer with filtering by tier, domain, status, and blind prediction flag.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
